data.description: INTERIOR PICTURES COMING 8/23...This expansive home sits on 1.3 acres and is located within city limits! An exceptional find, this home boosts over 7800 finished square feet of desirable living space! Complete with 5 bedrooms and 5 bathrooms, this 2 story home has so much to offer: great room, gourmet kitchen with SS appliances, pantry, large 4-season room, home office, rec room, and more! Head outside and find beautiful landscaping, multiple outdoor entertainment areas, heated and insulated garage, and an artificial putting green!
